# isp-core API Boundary

- For API feature work in `isp-core`, treat `zapi/` as the API source of truth.
- Add or modify API routes in `zapi/config/api_routes.php`.
- Add or modify API controllers, helpers, and utilities inside `zapi/` only.
- Do not move API code back into `app/Controllers/api`.

# Safety Rules

- Do not modify non-API web features in `app/Controllers` unless the user explicitly requests it.
- Keep existing web routes and web controllers behavior unchanged during API-only tasks.
- If a requested API change would require touching non-API web code, ask the user before proceeding.
